Hi Eddie,

The 215 clutch and pressure plate WILL NOT FIT into a 210mm flywheel.

I have used a 210mm and 215mm clutch on a 2L engine for two years now  
with no problem, even when pulling a fully laden westfakia with  
westrailer in tow.


